description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Sakura purrs with a rating of 73, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 73, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 8 for East, 8 for South, and 8 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10731-88880-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history.
